data.description: Step into a fresh, newly painted home that beams with pride of ownership. This well-maintained home comes with brand-new carpet throughout. One of the largest backyards in the neighborhood & it comes with a beautiful recently installed privacy fence. The oversized two-car detached garage is a spacious bonus. Enjoy modern living with included stainless steel appliances, covered with the Seller-provided home warranty included. Meticulously cared for, this home is truly a breath of fresh air. Schedule your showing today!
